                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-86-off487 t18300708-86-crimeloc490"></join>. The prisoner was in our employ - I have four pairs of trousers, some waistcoats, buttons, and drawers, which I got from different pawnbrokers; they are ours - we missed the cloth ones, but could not miss the others; they are part of our stock.</p>
